title: VENGEANCE ESSENTIAL HOUSE VOL.2
description:
VENGEANCE ESSENTIAL HOUSE VOL.2



This sequel is stuffed with everything you need to produce modern and contemporary
house sounds: tons of kicking bass drums, stretched e- and synthie basses, 
probably the widest variety of snares and wild real claps one can imagine, deep driving percussions, wicked fx, fresh crashs and rides, as well as crystal clear hihats and superb synths. Powerful house loops and inspiring melodies as mini construction kit spice up every production. Here you can find exactly the files you need for the professional production of up-to-date electro house, techhouse and progressive. This collection presents the ideal enlargement of every house sample pool. A must have for all owners of volume 1, but also a good choice for all vengeance newbies!



Professional house sample collection

Includes: drum sounds, hits, samples, bass, fx etc all arranged in style and structure
